{"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"role":"collection","modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"roleHeading":"Framework","externalID":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","symbolKind":"module","title":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" is the adapter between RevenueCat’s SDK and Swidux’s purchase-agnostic paywall plugin. The plugin owns paywall state (presentation flags, current entitlement, async progress); this package translates RevenueCat’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerInfo"},{"type":"text","text":" into the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EntitlementSnapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" the plugin expects, and surfaces the live "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerInfoStream"},{"type":"text","text":" so entitlement changes propagate without polling."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Two products ship together:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — ","type":"text"},{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (the live ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" conformer) and ","type":"text"},{"code":"MockRevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (a controllable preview \/ test conformer).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatPaywall(isPresented:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter(isPresented:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", drop-in SwiftUI view modifiers that wrap RevenueCatUI with platform-aware presentation, plus a ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatPaywall(state:send:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" convenience that composes both.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The flow:"}]},{"code":["View → store.send(.paywall(.request(reason:)))","  → PaywallPlugin sets isPresented = true","  → revenueCatPaywall observes the change, presents RevenueCatUI.PaywallView","  → user purchases → Purchases.shared.customerInfoStream yields a new CustomerInfo","  → RevenueCatPaywallService maps it to EntitlementSnapshot","  → PaywallPlugin reduces .customerInfoUpdated, sets isPro = true","  → store.paywall.isGateSatisfied flips, gated UI unlocks"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The plugin and the adapter stay decoupled: the plugin doesn’t know about RevenueCat, and the adapter doesn’t know about your action tree."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"RevenueCat adapter for Swidux’s "},{"code":"PaywallPlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Implements "},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" against ","type":"text"},{"code":"Purchases.shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", ships a controllable mock for previews and tests, and pairs with "},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for drop-in "},{"code":"PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterView"},{"type":"text","text":" presentation."}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Quickstart","anchor":"Quickstart","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/d